# Protonmail
IMAPAccount protonmail
Host 127.0.0.1
Port 1143
User philip.hartout@protonmail.com
#Alternatively you can enter a command to retrieve your password
PassCmd "gpg2 -q -d ~/.authinfo.protonmail.gpg | awk 'FNR == 1 {print $8}'"
SSLType NONE
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore remote
Account protonmail

#You can change .mail to something else
MaildirStore local
Path ~/.mail/protonmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/protonmail/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim
Flatten .

Channel inbox
Master :remote:
Slave :local:
Patterns *
Create Slave
#Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group protonmail
Channel inbox

